== Country Code Select

A simple country code select helper. Works exactly the same as country_select but uses country codes instead.

  country_code_select(:user, :country, [[ 'United States', 'US' ], [ 'Canada', 'CA' ]])

== Requirements

Rails 3+
Ruby 1.9.2+

